Academic Editor Project

This repository contains source-build scripts and public patch files for a
document editor runtime used by Tlooto-compatible WOPI hosts.

The runtime is built from upstream open-source office-editor source code under
the Mozilla Public License 2.0. This repository does not include Tlooto service
secrets, private WOPI host code, database code, user data, or proprietary API
logic.

User-facing product branding is intentionally changed to "Document Editor" /
"Document Engine". Required legal and copyright notices are preserved in this
repository and in the service's open-source notice page.
